weppsoilbuilder Module¶

class wepppy.webservices.weppsoilbuilder.WeppSoil_db(db_dir='./')¶

Bases: object

Provides fast querying of the whether a weppsoil exist for a particular mukey.

The mukeys.dat and mukeys_mask are arrays of mukeys and validity states packed with struct.pack. The mukeys in the dat array are sorted allowing for the use of bisect search.

The .dat files are built with scripts in wepppy.webservices.weppsoilbuildutils
